---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Cookie Policy — MyCGPA"
  description="Learn what cookies MyCGPA uses, including essential, analytics, and Google AdSense advertising cookies, and how to manage or opt out of them."
>
  <div class="legal-page">
    <div class="mesh-gradient" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="legal-hero container-page">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="display-xl page-title">Cookie Policy</h1>
        <p class="body-md subtitle">
          Last updated: July 7, 2026
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Legal Content -->
    <section class="legal-content container-page">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="toc-sidebar">
          <nav aria-label="Table of contents">
            <h2 class="toc-title">Contents</h2>
            <ul class="toc-list">
              <li><a href="#what-are-cookies">What Are Cookies</a></li>
              <li><a href="#types-of-cookies">Types of Cookies We Use</a></li>
              <li><a href="#google-adsense">Google AdSense &amp; Advertising</a></li>
              <li><a href="#google-analytics">Google Analytics</a></li>
              <li><a href="#manage-cookies">Manage Your Preferences</a></li>
              <li><a href="#browser-controls">Browser Controls</a></li>
              <li><a href="#changes">Changes to This Policy</a></li>
              <li><a href="#contact">Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
          </nav>
        </div>

        <div class="content-main card-level-2">
          <div class="legal-intro">
            <p class="body-lg">
              This Cookie Policy explains what cookies are, which ones MyCGPA uses, and how you can control them. It should be read alongside our <a href="/privacy/" class="email-link">Privacy Policy</a>.
            </p>
          </div>

          <section id="what-are-cookies" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">1. What Are Cookies</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              Cookies are small text files placed on your device when you visit a website. They are widely used to make websites work, work more efficiently, remember preferences, and to provide information to the site owners and their partners (such as advertising and analytics providers).
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="types-of-cookies" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">2. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
            <ul class="body-md">
              <li><strong>Strictly Necessary Cookies:</strong> Required for core site functionality, such as remembering your theme preference (light/dark) and your cookie consent choice. These cannot be disabled and do not require consent.</li>
              <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Set by Google Analytics to help us understand how visitors use the site (pages viewed, time on site, general location). These are only set if you accept cookies.</li>
              <li><strong>Advertising Cookies:</strong> Set by Google AdSense to serve and measure ads, and — if you consent — to personalize the ads you see based on your browsing activity. These are only set if you accept cookies.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section id="google-adsense" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">3. Google AdSense &amp; Advertising</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google, as a third-party vendor, uses cookies (such as the <code>IDE</code> and <code>test_cookie</code> cookies) to serve ads based on a user's prior visits to this and other websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your visit to our site and/or other sites on the Internet.
            </p>
            <p class="body-md">
              You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" class="email-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ads Settings</a>. Alternatively, you can opt out of a third-party vendor's use of cookies for personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" class="email-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.aboutads.info</a>, or if you're in the EU, <a href="https://www.youronlinechoices.eu/" class="email-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.youronlinechoices.eu</a>.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="google-analytics" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">4. Google Analytics</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              We use Google Analytics to understand aggregate site usage. Google Analytics sets cookies such as <code>_ga</code> and <code>_gid</code> to distinguish unique users and sessions. This data is anonymized where possible and is never combined with any grade, GPA, or CGPA data you enter into our calculators — that data never leaves your browser.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="manage-cookies" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">5. Manage Your Preferences</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              When you first visit MyCGPA, you'll see a cookie banner where you can accept all cookies or reject non-essential (analytics and advertising) cookies. Analytics and advertising cookies are only activated after you accept them.
            </p>
            <p class="body-md">
              You can change your mind at any time by clicking the button below to reopen the cookie preference banner.
            </p>
            <button type="button" id="reopen-cookie-banner" class="btn-secondary manage-btn">Manage Cookie Preferences</button>
          </section>

          <section id="browser-controls" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">6. Browser Controls</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              Most web browsers let you refuse or delete cookies through their settings. Refer to your browser's help documentation for instructions. Please note that blocking all cookies may affect certain site features, such as remembering your theme preference.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="changes" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in the cookies we use or for legal reasons. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page will reflect the most recent revision.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="contact" class="legal-section">
            <h2 class="display-md section-title">8. Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="body-md">
              If you have any questions about this Cookie Policy, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="contact-info">
              <p class="body-md">
                <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@mycgpa.com" class="email-link">support@mycgpa.com</a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="legal-cta container-page">
      <div class="cta-inner card-level-3">
        <h2 class="display-lg cta-title">Your privacy is protected</h2>
        <p class="body-md cta-desc">
          All calculations happen in your browser. Your grades stay private.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/#calculator" class="btn-primary">Try Calculator</a>
          <a href="/privacy/" class="btn-secondary">Privacy Policy</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<script>
  document.getElementById('reopen-cookie-banner')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    window.dispatchEvent(new Event('open-cookie-settings'));
    window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
  });
</script>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-5xl);
  }

  .legal-hero {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding-top: var(--spacing-4xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-title {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: var(--color-mute);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Content Layout */
  .legal-content {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-2xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Table of Contents */
  .toc-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
  }

  .toc-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-sm) 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .toc-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-xxs);
  }

  .toc-list a {
    display: block;
    padding: var(--spacing-xs) 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-body);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.15s ease;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .toc-list a:hover {
    color: var(--color-link);
  }

  /* Main Content */
  .content-main {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
  }

  .legal-intro {
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .legal-intro p {
    color: var(--color-body);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .legal-section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .section-title {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    scroll-margin-top: 100px;
  }

  .legal-section p {
    color: var(--color-body);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .legal-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .legal-section ul {
    margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;
    padding-left: var(--spacing-lg);
    color: var(--color-body);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .legal-section li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .legal-section strong {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .legal-section code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xs);
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .contact-info {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .contact-info p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .email-link {
    color: var(--color-link);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .email-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .manage-btn {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .legal-cta {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-4xl);
  }

  .cta-inner {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--spacing-3xl);
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-title {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .cta-desc {
    color: var(--color-body);
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-xl) 0;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 44px;
    padding: 0 var(--spacing-lg);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-on-primary);
    background-color: var(--color-ink);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 44px;
    padding: 0 var(--spacing-lg);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    background-color: var(--color-canvas);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline-strong);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 991px) {
    .content-wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .toc-sidebar {
      position: static;
      background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .toc-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: var(--spacing-xs);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .legal-hero {
      padding-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
    }

    .content-main {
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .toc-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 479px) {
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .btn-primary,
    .btn-secondary {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
